Colorectal cancer is an aggressive malignancy with a poor overall outcome.

 The purpose of this study is to evaluate the feasibility, safety and efficacy of neoadjuvant oxaliplatin, irinotecan combined with 5-fluorouraci/leucovorin or S-1 or capecitabine in patients with resectable colorectal cancer.

